{
  "version": "2",
  "title": "Londonium",
  "author": "Decent",
  "notes": "This profile simulates a Londinium R machines extraction style. This is an advanced profile with some added steps to assist with less than ideal puck prep. Christee-Lee described it as like having a milkshake with extra syrup. Great body and flavour range. 2nd edition.  This is identical to the LRv2 profile, but renamed to be easier to understand. By Damian Brakel",
  "beverage_type": "espresso",
  "steps": [
